mdRecord.dcterms:title: Harvestwood Cemetery, Little River Dist.
mdRecord.dcterms:description:
This well maintained cemetery is located on the northwest corner of Franklin Pike SE and Harvestwood Rd SE next to the Harvestwood Covenant Prebyterian Church at 2391 Franklin Pike SE. SE. It is Visible from Google Earth and Google Maps.
